[
  {
    "startTime": 15.26,
    "endTime": 18.259,
    "text": "My travels to Afghanistan"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.26,
    "endTime": 21.26,
    "text": "began many, many years ago"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.26,
    "endTime": 24.26,
    "text": "on the eastern border of my country,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.26,
    "endTime": 27.26,
    "text": "my homeland, Poland."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.26,
    "endTime": 29.26,
    "text": "I was walking through the forests"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.26,
    "endTime": 33.260000000000005,
    "text": "of my grandmother's tales."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.26,
    "endTime": 38.26,
    "text": "A land where every field hides a grave,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.26,
    "endTime": 40.26,
    "text": "where millions of people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.26,
    "endTime": 43.26,
    "text": "have been deported or killed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.26,
    "endTime": 46.26,
    "text": "in the 20th century."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.26,
    "endTime": 48.26,
    "text": "Behind the destruction,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.26,
    "endTime": 51.26,
    "text": "I found a soul of places."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.26,
    "endTime": 53.26,
    "text": "I met humble people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.26,
    "endTime": 55.26,
    "text": "I heard their prayer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.26,
    "endTime": 57.26,
    "text": "and ate their bread."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.26,
    "endTime": 62.26,
    "text": "Then I have been walking East for 20 years --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.26,
    "endTime": 65.259,
    "text": "from Eastern Europe to Central Asia --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.26,
    "endTime": 67.26,
    "text": "through the Caucasus Mountains,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.26,
    "endTime": 69.26,
    "text": "Middle East,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.26,
    "endTime": 71.26,
    "text": "North Africa,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.26,
    "endTime": 73.26,
    "text": "Russia."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.26,
    "endTime": 77.26,
    "text": "And I ever met more humble people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.26,
    "endTime": 80.26,
    "text": "And I shared their bread and their prayer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.26,
    "endTime": 83.26,
    "text": "This is why I went to Afghanistan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.26,
    "endTime": 87.26,
    "text": "One day, I crossed the bridge"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.26,
    "endTime": 89.26,
    "text": "over the Oxus River."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.26,
    "endTime": 91.26,
    "text": "I was alone on foot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.26,
    "endTime": 93.26,
    "text": "And the Afghan soldier was so surprised to see me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.26,
    "endTime": 96.26,
    "text": "that he forgot to stamp my passport."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.26,
    "endTime": 98.26,
    "text": "But he gave me a cup of tea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.26,
    "endTime": 100.26,
    "text": "And I understood"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.26,
    "endTime": 103.26,
    "text": "that his surprise was my protection."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.26,
    "endTime": 106.26,
    "text": "So I have been walking and traveling,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.26,
    "endTime": 109.26,
    "text": "by horses, by yak, by truck, by hitchhiking,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.26,
    "endTime": 111.26,
    "text": "from Iran's border"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.26,
    "endTime": 116.26,
    "text": "to the bottom, to the edge of the Wakhan Corridor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.26,
    "endTime": 118.26,
    "text": "And in this way"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.26,
    "endTime": 125.26,
    "text": "I could find noor, the hidden light of Afghanistan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.26,
    "endTime": 127.26,
    "text": "My only weapon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.26,
    "endTime": 132.26,
    "text": "was my notebook and my Leica."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.26,
    "endTime": 134.26,
    "text": "I heard prayers of the Sufi --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.26,
    "endTime": 136.26,
    "text": "humble Muslims,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.26,
    "endTime": 138.26,
    "text": "hated by the Taliban."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.26,
    "endTime": 140.26,
    "text": "Hidden river,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.26,
    "endTime": 142.26,
    "text": "interconnected with the mysticism"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.26,
    "endTime": 145.26,
    "text": "from Gibraltar to India."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.26,
    "endTime": 150.26,
    "text": "The mosque where the respectful foreigner"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.26,
    "endTime": 152.26,
    "text": "is showered with blessings"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.26,
    "endTime": 155.26,
    "text": "and with tears,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.26,
    "endTime": 159.26,
    "text": "and welcomed as a gift."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.26,
    "endTime": 161.26,
    "text": "What do we know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.26,
    "endTime": 163.26,
    "text": "about the country and the people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.26,
    "endTime": 166.26,
    "text": "that we pretend to protect,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.26,
    "endTime": 169.26,
    "text": "about the villages"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.26,
    "endTime": 171.26,
    "text": "where the only one medicine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.26,
    "endTime": 173.26,
    "text": "to kill the pain and to stop the hunger"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.26,
    "endTime": 175.26,
    "text": "is opium?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.26,
    "endTime": 178.26,
    "text": "These are opium-addicted people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.26,
    "endTime": 181.26,
    "text": "on the roofs of Kabul"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.26,
    "endTime": 185.26,
    "text": "10 years after the beginning of our war."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.26,
    "endTime": 188.26,
    "text": "These are the nomad girls"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.26,
    "endTime": 192.26,
    "text": "who became prostitutes for Afghan businessmen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.26,
    "endTime": 194.26,
    "text": "What do we know about the women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.26,
    "endTime": 196.26,
    "text": "10 years after the war?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.26,
    "endTime": 198.26,
    "text": "Clothed in this nylon bag,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.26,
    "endTime": 200.26,
    "text": "made in China,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.26,
    "endTime": 204.26,
    "text": "with the name of burqa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.26,
    "endTime": 206.26,
    "text": "I saw one day,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.26,
    "endTime": 209.26,
    "text": "the largest school in Afghanistan,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.26,
    "endTime": 211.26,
    "text": "a girls' school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.26,
    "endTime": 214.26,
    "text": "13,000 girls"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.26,
    "endTime": 218.26,
    "text": "studying here"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.26,
    "endTime": 221.26,
    "text": "in the rooms underground,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.26,
    "endTime": 224.26,
    "text": "full of scorpions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.26,
    "endTime": 227.26,
    "text": "And their love [for studying]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.26,
    "endTime": 232.26,
    "text": "was so big that I cried."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.26,
    "endTime": 234.26,
    "text": "What do we know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.26,
    "endTime": 237.26,
    "text": "about the death threats by the Taliban"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.26,
    "endTime": 239.26,
    "text": "nailed on the doors"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.26,
    "endTime": 245.26,
    "text": "of the people who dare to send their daughters to school as in Balkh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.26,
    "endTime": 248.26,
    "text": "The region is not secure, but full of the Taliban,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.26,
    "endTime": 250.26,
    "text": "and they did it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.26,
    "endTime": 252.26,
    "text": "My aim is to give a voice"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.26,
    "endTime": 255.26,
    "text": "to the silent people,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.26,
    "endTime": 259.26,
    "text": "to show the hidden lights"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.26,
    "endTime": 262.26,
    "text": "behind the curtain of the great game,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.26,
    "endTime": 265.26,
    "text": "the small worlds ignored by the media"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.26,
    "endTime": 267.26,
    "text": "and the prophets of a global conflict."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.26,
    "endTime": 269.26,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.26,
    "endTime": 278.26,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  }
]